post_text: [ALERT] To minimize the opportunities for transmission of COVID-19, RCHS will be closed to students beginning Monday, March 16. post_text:
We had a wonderful day catching up with our Forever Phoenix during our 20th Anniversary Celebration on June 15! Thank you to the many, many alumni and alumni parents who returned to Raleigh Charter to reconnect and reminisce with us. We love talking to our alumni and learning about all the great things they have been up to!

We'd like to say a huge thank you to Catherine Davis Photography for spending the day with us and capturing so many special moments! We've posted a photo album here on our Facebook page and you can also view (and download!) even more photos through this online gallery: http://www.catherinedavisphotography.com/proofing/rchs-20th

To download an image without the watermark:
--Provide an email to get started.
--Select the image you want
--Click on the download icon- far right with a down arrow and a line. (Images are downloaded one at a time.)

The 2018 Phoenix Annual Newsletter is here! We are excited to release the digital edition today! The theme of this year's newsletter is Celebrating 20 Years Together. In honor of our 20th Anniversary year, we are highlighting the many wonderful ways our students, alumni, teachers, staff, and parents come together to build our community.

We invite you to read the newsletter online and share it with your family and friends. All current and alumni families will receive a printed copy of the newsletter within the coming weeks. Click here to read: https://www.raleighcharterhs.org/Alumni/PhoenixAnnualNewsletter2018.pdf
